{"tid":1536014,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京之旅求指點","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:31:23.000Z","uid":88835,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a739e0ebcd98bdd681a7eb062874eaad4298c5df","tid":1536014,"uid":88835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"黎緊想同屋企人去東京<br />\n想問下有咩景點特別推介？<br />\n做左research睇過下河口湖睇富士山好似好靚<br />\n但因為買左酒店係大久保站既東京新宿百日酒店<br />\n應該只可以即日來回咁去玩 應該玩唔到咁多行程？<br />\n我打算plan朝早搭巴士出發去到河口湖站<br />\n買天上山公園纜車+遊船+周遊巴士券<br />\n其實係咪已經霸左一日？<br />\n仲有其他想去既地方就係富士山五合目<br />\n忍野八海 同埋 outlet 想請教下可唔可以加到入行程呢？<br />\n新手第一次去東京 有啲迷惘 <br />\n請咁多位巴打指點一下迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外有咩特別推介都可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ac3c1e7a58b1c4339844e4b9a291d6cc61cf60","tid":1536014,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-s